{"tid":497580,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"Busking究竟要幾時練幾時夾？","createTime":"2017-12-13T02:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T03:11:39.000Z","uid":108894,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ed887f783787b5c717567fe117afc02336d55b82","tid":497580,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:21:25.000Z","msg":"話說我有教會朋友打算約埋我busking<br />\n話晒busking都係出街唱比人聽，為左唔想質素太差，佢地又好認真咁我當然追問下幾時練幾時夾，但佢嘅答覆係&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0yhb2lnp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0yhb2lnp&h=ae527128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我屌咩，你而家夾band式busking，你又要試flow又要剩，又要練熟D樂器，又要同主唱夾，你老味你同我講出發前夾下就算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢唔係教會嘅朋友，我當堂已經屌7左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，既然係夾band busking就同我事前準備認真少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e1e728d3e49615bbd1f17ec82a26df088d381e","tid":497580,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:23:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca0ed8e65ca0a1eb1753ebf3a0ddf12cba1b52a6","tid":497580,"uid":159258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:25:27.000Z","msg":"夾開既話真係去之前夾下就得"},{"pid":"db4e6812bae5717bc661bb65bcf84f48b23117ac","tid":497580,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:26:04.000Z","msg":"唔好出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n盞出醜"},{"pid":"4d25984ce65b383a2c140f713b940a6c0ccfb173","tid":497580,"uid":31901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"阿豬阿狗都話自己busking <br />\n同旺角跳大媽舞班八婆無分別<br />\n滿足個人私欲"},{"pid":"2342fa4e1de70402ae5a56dfae59c4358a0af400","tid":497580,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夾開既話真係去之前夾下就得</blockquote><br />\n當然唔是啦<img src=\"/asset